Reserve 1 Tbsp. nuts. Finely chop remaining nuts; mix with wafer crumbs and butter. Press onto bottom and up side of 9-inch tart pan or shallow pie plate. Beat pudding mix and milk with whisk 2 min. Stir in COOL WHIP. Spoon into crust. Refrigerate 3 hours or until firm. Top with fruit and reserved nuts just before serving.